{
  "stem": "11671.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he just said now to calm down and to just take what's, you know, best for us, to keep our minds and, and our heads straight and get the clothes and the food that we can take with us.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we, you know, we tried to take our souvenirs, and we couldn't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We used to have these beautiful awards from school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were like little tins if you did, you know, well in school, gold tins.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we wanted to take them, and they said, no, you can't take any pictures or anything else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Just take food and warm clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all put on several layers of clothing, and we were told to go out to the courtyard in 20 minutes or else.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the soldier just, you know, showed his gun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we knew very well what he meant to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to obey.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- How old were you at that time?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 17.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he marched us out in the courtyard, and we waited until everybody was gathered from that immediate community, and we were the very first street in Kolozsvar to be taken.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember I didn't have my good walking shoes, so I went over to the soldier and asked him if I could go get my good shoes, because I just had sandals.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, you can go get it from the shoemaker, which was just down the block.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I'll have to walk with you so you will not escape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he walked with me down to the shoemaker to get my shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My family was lined up in the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
